DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
     The iissssppaaccee() function tests for the standard white-space characters.  In
     the ASCII character set, this includes the following characters:


     011 ht        012 nl        013 vt        014 np        015 cr
     040 sp

RREETTUURRNN VVAALLUUEESS
     The iissssppaaccee() function returns zero if the character tests false and re-
     turns non-zero if the character tests true.

